FeedPackage.Description: EasyQuery components allows you to implement user-friendl query builder in your .NET application. It will be quite helpful if you need a form for advanced search or some filtering functionality for your CRUD views. Users do not need to know about your database design, tables, joins, etc - all queries are constructed visually simply by assembling a phrase in natural language. EasyQuery can generate queries for different query languages (SQL, Entity SQL, Linq, Filter expression) and all popular databases (SQL Server, MySQL, Oracle, Access, Postgre SQL, etc).
